  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.7">
<l>maṟantikaḻu maṉamoḻittu vañca māṟṟi</l>
<l>yaimpulaṉka ḷaṭakkiyiṭarp pārat tuṉpam</l>
<l>tuṟantirumup poḻutētti yellai yillāt</l>
<l>toṉṉeṟikka ṇilainiṉṟa toṇṭa rāṉa</l>
<l>aṟantikaḻu maṉattavartaṅ katiyaip poṉṉi</l>
<l>yaṇiyaraṅkat taravaṇaiyiṟ paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>niṟantikaḻu māyōṉaik kaṇṭeṉ kaṇkaḷ</l>
<l>nīrmalka veṉṟukolō niṟku nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day [I will] stand [there] as my eyes fill with tears, having seen</l>
<l>Māyōṉ of glowing lustre, who sleeps on the serpent-bed in Raṅgam,</l>
<l>which Poṉṉi decorates, the Refuge of</l>
<l rend="indent">those with hearts where dharma shines,</l>
<l rend="indent">who are servants who have stood steadfastly on the infinitely ancient path,</l>
<l rend="indent">ridding the mind of violence that it contains and curing [it of its] deceit,</l>
<l rend="indent">controlling the five senses, renouncing the affliction [caused by] the burden of trouble,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] praising five times [a day]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
